===Etymology===
From {{confix|xeno|phobe}}. From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ξένος|tr=xenos||foreign, strange|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}, + {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|φόβος||fear|tr=phobos|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# One who [[fear]]s that which is [[unknown]]; one who fears [[people]] who are [[different]] from [[oneself]], [[especially]] in the case of [[foreign]] people

